decks.notes: This deck focuses on using aggressive tactics and powerful synergy between the commanders Rograkh, Son of Rohgahh and Tevesh Szat, Doom of Fools. It includes a wide variety of low-cost spells and creatures that can quickly build up a threatening board presence. The deck also utilizes powerful black and red cards to disrupt the opponent's game plan and control the battlefield. By combining the strengths of both commanders and carefully managing resources, the deck aims to overwhelm the opponent and secure a quick victory. The key strategy is to maintain pressure on the opponent while efficiently utilizing the deck's resources to consistently stay ahead in the game.
